## Add Failover Cluster

### A small problem
When I add the nodes to failover cluster, an error is reported 'The node cannot be detected'.
It looks like net connection problem. 
ping
From nodes(101, 102, 103) to domain controller(100) -- Connected
From domain controller(100) to nodes(101, 102, 103) -- fail
From nodes(101, 102, 103) to nodes(101, 102, 103)   -- fail
So the connection is one way only.
The solution is 
```
TURN OFF FIREWALL
```
Three IT artifact: restart, cut off and turn off firewall. Three artifacts on hand, keep warnings away.
记得补个图
